				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-T%E1%BA%AFc/%C4%90%E1%BB%93-ch%C3%AD-ca/poem--A3qpFL2UYH8DOEkrBgXVg">Đồ chí ca - 圖誌歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-T%E1%BA%AFc/author-SdALrlg8daTfB8oNiho-Nw">Lê Tắc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi-Nghi-Sinh/H%C3%A0m-ti%E1%BA%BFu-hoa/poem-DXiPojvRlnrsGrxeRRS8BA">Hàm tiếu hoa - 含笑花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi-Nghi-Sinh/author-AB4c7k5T7qtBpZQ5UmKnEg">Thi Nghi Sinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/H%C3%AD-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Xu-Ng%C3%B4n-th%E1%BA%A3o-c%C3%A1c-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1xg3hi80FKcKoSCSEece2g">Hí đề Xu Ngôn thảo các tam thập nhị vận - 戲題樞言草閣三十二韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Kho%C3%A1-ti%E1%BB%83u-th%E1%BB%A5-s%E1%BB%AB-ch%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-x%C3%A1-b%E1%BA%AFc-qu%E1%BA%A3-l%C3%A2m-chi-m%E1%BA%A1n-hoang-u%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%8Bnh-ng%E1%BA%ADt-di-s%C3%A0ng-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-uy0OytEkeLLQ9VSomgIAgg">Khoá tiểu thụ sừ chước xá bắc quả lâm, chi mạn hoang uế, tịnh ngật di sàng kỳ 1 - 課小豎鋤斫舍北果林，枝蔓荒穢，淨訖移床三首其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-Lan-T%C3%ADnh-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/Nam-kha-t%E1%BB%AD-C%E1%BB%95-th%C3%BA-c%C6%A1-%C3%B4-t%E1%BA%ADp/poem-dnFR0pq8VoWlmp1ZZEvMQg">Nam kha tử (Cổ thú cơ ô tập) - 南歌子（古戍饑烏集）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-Lan-T%C3%ADnh-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-4UIcOQq3X5B-YNUldGF_5g">Nạp Lan Tính Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-V%E1%BB%8B-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/S%E1%BB%A9-L%C4%A9nh-Nam-v%C4%83n-Th%C3%B4i-M%C3%A3-nh%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-s%E1%BB%AD-b%C3%ADnh-b%C3%A1